parameters:
A wounded fugitive: 'I have nightmares every night. Burned
ships, charred corpses... There were no heroes in that
place.'

The man who escaped from conscription said, I can't fight
for someone else. I can only live for myself, so that's why
I ran away.

The man who escaped from conscription said, I can't fight
for someone else, I can only live for myself, that's why I
ran away.

Captain Clevo: There's a new bloodstain... It seems like
we're in the right place.

Captain Clevo: In this situation, tell me how I should act
as I follow Clea's lead.

Clea: Please block off the escape route. We've come this
far, we can't let them get away.
Captain Clevo: Is it okay for you all to engage in combat?

Clea: If we lose, Captain Clevo, please make sure to stop
the Dayley's short sword.

Clea: In the meantime, Cors and the others should be
arriving.
Clea: I will go ahead, so please take care of things.
Captain Clevo: Clea is a good leader.
Clea: Yes! She's my precious friend!
Captain Clevo: Let's go inside too.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Traveling Merchant: Even if someone poor is living there...
just that alone makes it a valuable place for a merchant.

Traveling Merchant: Even if someone poor is living there...
just that alone makes it a valuable place for a merchant.
Former leader of the thief gang, Gift: You all...

Former leader of the thief gang, Gift: You guys... It seems
like you're still pursuing the adventurer's life. I, too,
have been traveling throughout the empire while taking on
freelance requests.

Former leader of the thief gang, Gift: It's not bad to be
appreciated... For the time being, I'll continue living this
way.

Former leader of the thief gang, Gift: It's a token of
gratitude from my former subordinates. Please accept it if
you'd like.

Former leader of the thief gang, Gift: Please take care of
my husband and former subordinates.

Dan the loser: Are you Ginger's messenger? If not, sorry,
but I can't let you in.

Dan, the loser dog: Could you help me carry the package I
received from Grandpa Ginger inside?

Sister Eleo: Leave it to me. I'll take care of it in place
of Grandpa Ginger.

Dan, the loser dog: He's like a monk straight out of a
painting... and that beautiful woman next to him looks like
she's wearing a costume for monk enthusiasts on Prostitution
Island.

Monk Sophia: Oh my, hehe, not only in appearance but also
in personality, I'm not limited to being just a monk, you
know?

Sister Eleo: Sophia-san! I'm sure I've told you multiple
times not to mess up your appearance!

Dan, the loser dog: Ahaha, they're energetic young ladies.
Not to brag, but this place is a rundown shack, so please be
careful with the floor, okay?
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Drunk man: Hic... Could you bless me with just one drink?

Drunk man: Hic... Oh, are you going to bless me with a
drink?

Priestess Sophia: Yes, of course. How about starting with a
meal before the drink?
Priestess Sophia: I am preparing the finest drink for you.

Drunk man: You do have a point... Let's start with a meal
then.

Mage Relm: There wasn't any alcohol, right? Are you
planning to give him your own wine?

Drunk man: It's been a while since I had a proper meal. So,
can I have a little treat?

Priestess Sophia: Yes, of course. This will be the finest
drink.
Drunk man: It looks transparent for a wine.

Priestess Sophia: No, no, it has a beautiful color, doesn't
it?
Mage Relm: Y-Yes. It's the color of wine!

Drunk man: This is delicious! Oh, it's been a while since I
had such high-quality sake!
Mage Relm: What kind of magic did you use!?

Priestess Sophia: I'll ask you something strange. A heavily
drunk person can't distinguish between wine and water, you
know.
Mage Relm: Sigh... Sophia-san, please be careful too.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Drunk man: Hic... Could you bless me with just one drink?
